content.comment:
New supplemental materials have been added to the appendix of the paper, and we will continue to update the paper before the rebuttal deadline.

Mainly update:
1. The pseudo-code;
2. The training time of LLSQ;
3. The simulated gradient formulation of the scaling factors and the bit-shift quantization formulation.

